Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:06.70,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.909,859.091)\fade(255,0,255,0,1435,4780,5620)}The Crisis of Ten Attendants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginseng soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I see it, the emperor will\Nonly last for another two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The emperor favors Liú Xié,\Nnaturally he'd like for him to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Liú Biàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Empress Hé and Hé Jìn\Nwill just leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:08.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(184.091,605.455)\fade(255,0,255,0,445,2340,2700)}Duàn Guī
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, our first plan is\N to deal with Hé Jìn. When he dies, Empress Hé-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What can she do?\NEverything she has she owes to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:32.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.182,548.182)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,1540,2302)}Empress Dowager\NDǒng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine spirits hear me.\NBless his majesty with a speedy recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to trade the years I have left\Nfor the emperor to have a few more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless his majesty, divine spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless his majesty, divine spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless his majesty, divine spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411.137,713.864)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,2020,2340)}Liú Xié
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother.\NNo... Empress Dowager, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely be a good emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless his majesty, divine spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1217.045,707.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1780,2140)}Empress Hé
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1174.091,685.227)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,2050,2460)}Liú Biàn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects to Empress Dowager Dǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects to Empress Hé!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(218.863,568.636)\fade(255,0,255,0,520,260,2940)}Jiàn Shuò
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Hé Jìn reached the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably still on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill all who leaks the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, don't enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty summoned me, how could I not go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty has passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ten Attendants are keeping it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, sir, they intend to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(243.116,649.87)\fade(255,0,255,0,520,1980,2500)}Zhāng Ràng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who leaked the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiǎn Shuò, make sure to step up security!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll personally see to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hé Jìn still wants to enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only to force Liú Biàn onto the imperial throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be a momentous day! We must all speak as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those rotten eunuchs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will exterminate them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, please calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.50,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(257.727,703.636)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,1950,2500)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The eunuchs' power has been growing since the reigns of Emperors Chōng and Zhì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Their influence spreads all across the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Their power didn't accumulate overnight,\Nnor can it be taken down overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(249.545,689.611)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1500,2020)}Hé Jìn\NStyled: Suìgāo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't keep this a secret,\Nwe'll be the ones eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Generalissimo, reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a subordinate. What would you know of imperial court affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The late emperor favored Jiǎn Shuò.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiǎn Shuò and Empress Dowager Dǒng have a close relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by putting blame on Jiǎn Shuò,\Ncan we still save our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! Correct! Blame it all on Jiǎn Shuò!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, we need hurry over to Empress Hé,\Ngrovel before her, and beg for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only one who\Nhas the power to save us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,\Nyou are to hurry over to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Return ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the imperial guardsmen are\N under the command of Jiǎn Shuò.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried they've already set an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}We should first install the rightful emperor, then wipe out the eunuchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Mèngdé, your words quite suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Who dares assist me and eliminate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Give me 5,000 elite troops, to enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Coronate the rightful emperor, then kill the eunuchs and restore peace to the realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With Běnchū's help, I can rest assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon all the ministers to gather at the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Sir, ambushes outside the court have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}We dare not venture further inside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Why don't we eliminate \N the eunuchs and purge the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Restore peace to the realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Generalissimo, stick to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Crown the emperor first,\Nthen purge the eunuchs afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Mèngdé is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}the nation can't go on without its leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}We should crown the new emperor right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This minister requests the Crown Prince to ascend the throne immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your minister, Hé Jìn, congratulates\N the Crown Prince on his ascension to the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't trust those high officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand court affairs better than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The plot to murder you \Nwas orchestrated by Jiǎn Shuò alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Ràng and the others had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you favor Zhāng Ràng and his ilk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We come from a poor background.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for Zhāng Ràng and his\N faction, could we be where we are today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying wealth and prestige?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,where's this Jiǎn Shuò now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You all may come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, spare our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, spare our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, it was Jiǎn Shuò who\Ncollaborated with Grand-Empress Dowager Dǒng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The plot against you, Generalissimo, had nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That villain Jiǎn Shuò has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We present you his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Generalissimo for the sake\Nof our past friendship, spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll wait for the\NGeneralissimo's orders before acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We swear our loyalty! We would never consider betraying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiǎn Shuò has already been punished for his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you believe the words of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They are truly innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the Empress Dowager,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be spared this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be a next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you plot to kill me again, I won't be as merciful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Generalissimo! We wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiǎn Shuò has been eliminated for his plot against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, Zhāng Ràng\Nsimply shifted the blame to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to let\Nthe Ten Attendants get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Jiǎn Shuò's entire family put to death! Exterminate them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the rest of the eunuchs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't remove the eunuchs now, there will be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My decision is final! This talk is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-Empress Dowager,\Ndon't hurt your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You all served as the servants of the late majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The late emperor favored and raised you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all mute now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager, the late Emperor's bones are barely even cold yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't dare to harm\Nthe Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still the Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That Empress Dowager Hé, although it was her son who became Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she still has to show respect\Nto the Grand-Empress Dowager,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of His Majesty's passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Grand-Empress Dowager\Nwished to say something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you could demote some officials,\Neven Hé Jìn and Empress Hé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd dare to disobey you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand-Empress Dowager\Nis still the Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hé Jìn just established Biàn as the emperor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was only one step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-Empress Dowager, don't give in.\NWhy not take your own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by 'take your own way?'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Empress Dowager Hé has Prince Biàn;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Grand-Empress Dowager, don't you have Prince Xié?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Empress Dowager Hé has her elder brother Hé Jìn;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Grand-Empress Dowager, don't you have your own maternal relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}In my opinion, it's better to act sooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Tomorrow morning, before the Imperial Court,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}the Grand-Empress Dowager may confer the title Prince of Chénliú upon Prince Xié
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}and appoint her nephew Dǒng Chòng\Nthe General of Flying Cavalry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}in order to check their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Good,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}I'll hold court from behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:20.55,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Women weren't allowed to attend the court. However, it was an open secret that many Empresses did so from 'behind the curtain'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, without Generalissimo's presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand-Empress Dowager suddenly appeared in court to listen to the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an imperial decree conferring the title Price of Chénliú on Prince Xié.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and promoting Dǒng Chòng to {\i1}General of Flying Cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Emphasis was also given for the Ten Attendants\Nto manage the affairs of state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If this isn't the work of the Ten Attendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's the Grand-Empress Dowager causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll go to the palace to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, I don't think this matter has anything to do with the Ten Attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything about it. \NThink about it, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Biàn succeeded the throne, how could the Grand-Empress Dowager not be angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Generalissimo,\Nin control of all military forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she not be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure her intentions are
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing more than to make a move against our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Zhāng Ràng and the eunuchs swore allegiance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They were spared and wouldn't dare act against me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand-Empress Dowager is weak and isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for her to try and\Ngain the support of the Ten Attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we use this opportunity to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,persuade Grand-Empress Dowager Dǒng\Nto stay out of court affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're family, talk frankly.\NThere is no need to be formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Empress, you and I are women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not appropriate to be interfering with court affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past when Empress Lǚ held power she interfered with court affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:12.00,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Empress Lǚ dominated early Hàn politics for 15 years through brutality and the use of puppet emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, more than a thousand of her family members were executed; her clan exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you and I should just live\Npeacefully inside the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and let the veteran ministers discuss court affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what is best for the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely hope you will listen\Ncarefully to your daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare attempt to lecture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my recommendation,\Ncould you even be here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would your son have become the Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter-in-law wouldn't dare to.\NI only wanted to remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,First you were jealous of Beauty Wáng\Nand had her poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:05.80,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Beauty Wáng was a favored concubine of the late Emperor and the mother of Liú Xié.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to kill me now as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dare keep speaking this nonsense,\NI'll have Dǒng Zhòng kill you and your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to advise you reasonably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress-Mother, why are you so unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to speak about being unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous, truly ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress-Mother, better watch your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,True, I came from a poor background.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Empress-Mother, \Nyou used to be only a concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for your son \Nsucceeding Emperor Xiàohuán,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,could you become the national mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Given our current roles,\Nperhaps it's best to not mention our past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with being a concubine?\NThis concubine is a hundred times better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe before, but not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so different between then and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare to kill Empress Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only capable of daring to kill pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If a junior slighted an elder\Nwouldn't that be a major offense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the Emperor is going to punish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use the Emperor to threaten me.\NI'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Grand-Empress Dowager,\Nwhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Grand-Empress Dowager Dǒng\Nhaving been a concubine,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}is unfit to reside in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}With the death of the late emperor,\Nthere is less reason for her to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}She is to return to her hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}and leave for Héjiān effectively immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand-Empress Dowager is not used to your crude meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Generalissimo has sent this imperial wine to honor the Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please drink and enjoy, Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-Empress Dowager! The wine is poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Grand-Empress Dowager, drink the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.97,0:26:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand-Empress Dowager\Nhas been poisoned by Hé Jìn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.25,0:26:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hé Jìn, that pig butcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he murder the state mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.10,0:26:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrogant miscreant!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If wasn't for us, he wouldn't be where he is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.22,0:26:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains that backed us have collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.47,0:26:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we act from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.75,0:26:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only see the wind and steer the helm,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.10,0:26:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or we could join up with Hé Jìn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.02,0:26:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way... nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.45,0:26:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Hé Jìn may not have grand ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.62,0:26:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which of the high officials\Nbacking him doesn't hates us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.92,0:26:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,would Hé Jìn dare enthrone the new\N emperor during the late one's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.87,0:26:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now today, he poisoned the Grand-Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.52,0:27:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't act now, we'll be endangered!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.82,0:27:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by removing Hé Jìn first,\Ncan the others be brought into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.29,0:27:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All our power lies inside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.50,0:27:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We must keep control over the\NEmperor or the Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we can do as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.65,0:27:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the Empress Dowager,\Nwe need to be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.38,0:27:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we can handle the three royals,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.70,0:27:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hé Jìn will fall easily as turning over the palm of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Why shouldn't I want to kill the eunuchs?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:28:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}The Empress Dowager says\Nthe eunuchs are capable administrators,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}that their mandate was established since the prior reign and shouldn't be disregarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}And since we're still in mourning for the late Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}It's disrespectful to the shrine of the forefathers to kill veteran servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.40,0:28:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}What can I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.65,0:28:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Indecision will cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.25,0:28:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Generalissimo, I, Běnchū, and all the other generals are all ready for your commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Zhāng Ràng is spreading rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.02,0:28:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Why don't we use this excuse to execute them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.62,0:28:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}We shouldn't waste this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.85,0:28:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}The Empress Dowager would never go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.55,0:28:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Generalissimo, you may summon some frontier troops to enter the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.46,0:28:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Use them to exterminate the eunuchs, and ignore the Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.97,0:28:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.07,0:28:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really excellent plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.96,0:28:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the Registrar; Chén Lín!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.54,0:29:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the Registrar; Chén Lín!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.77,0:29:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,\NI went and told my brother to spare your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.21,0:29:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still afraid I can't keep your old lives safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.90,0:29:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress Dowager humours us!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.22,0:29:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With you protecting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.06,0:29:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom can compare with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.99,0:29:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.82,0:29:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Cáo Cāo pays his respects to the Generalissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.00,0:29:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Generalissimo,\Nit's an easy matter to remove the eunuchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.95,0:29:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}A warden is equal to the task, why summon a frontier army?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.95,0:29:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}A warden is enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.80,0:29:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}A warden is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.42,0:30:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}All of the issues come from the ringleaders. No need to exterminate everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.52,0:30:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}If we want to kill everyone,\Nthe plot will leak out, and we'll certainly fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.52,0:30:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Oh... I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.00,0:30:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}Mèngdé is related to the eunuchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.50,0:30:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}It's only natural for him to be soft on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.11,0:30:26.48,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: Cáo Cāo's father, Cáo Sōng was adopted by the eunuch Cáo Téng.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.35,0:30:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.98,0:30:32.50,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(267.955,699.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,5000,5000)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.07,0:30:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(727.014,893.571)}The one who ruins the nation, be none other than Hé Jìn!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:39.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.279,668.864)\fade(255,0,255,0,540,2180,2620)}Dīng Yuán\NStyled: Jiànyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.70,0:30:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó is on the table to remove the eunuchs?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.90,0:30:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who doesn't know his relation with the Ten Attendants?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.87,0:30:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Yellow Turban Rebellion,\Nhe was defeated and suffered heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.92,0:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for the Ten Attendants' favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how could he have replaced Director Lú?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.22,0:31:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, Huángfǔ Sōng testified to your merits, Director Lú.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.62,0:31:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, Zigān, how could you be here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.95,0:31:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó is coming with 200,000 armored troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.25,0:31:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The eunuchs are about to be swept away as easily as turning over the palm of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.20,0:31:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, Dǒng Zhuó is a rabid wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.42,0:31:36.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300.085,370.227)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,2150,2540)}Zhèng Tài
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him in the capital, and he will eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.02,0:31:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.95,0:31:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't possibly be able to do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.98,0:31:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.65,0:31:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.54,0:31:48.70,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.182,771.136)\fade(255,0,255,0,520,2750,3140)}Lú Zhí\NStyled: Zǐgān
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.95,0:31:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He may seems kind\Nbut is cruel as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.27,0:31:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in the capital,\Nhe will bring disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.32,0:31:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to stop him from\Nentering the capital to avoid chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.57,0:32:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all just pedantic opinions!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.58,0:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.65,0:32:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The order has been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.30,0:32:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can no longer bear this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.20,0:32:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.95,0:32:37.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Abandon your post and flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.58,0:32:58.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1185.95,677.923)\fade(255,0,255,0,375,2150,2500)}Dǒng Zhuó\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Generalissimo has ordered\Nfrontier armies to enter the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.38,0:33:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans to kill us! Please save our lives,\NEmpress Dowager, we beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans to kill us! Please save our lives,\NEmpress Dowager, we beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.47,0:33:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.42,0:33:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.67,0:33:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.55,0:33:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You all head over to the Generalissimo's\Nresidence and admit your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.97,0:33:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and speak well on your behalf again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.65,0:33:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.86,0:33:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we servants wouldn't dare go to the\NGeneralissimo's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.53,0:33:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go over to his residence to admit our crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:33:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be crushed into dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Empress Dowager! Summon the Generalissimo to enter the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.30,0:34:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can be before you when we admit our crimes to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.12,0:34:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.25,0:34:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.30,0:34:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Generalissimo still won't forgive us,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.15,0:34:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd rather die before our Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.72,0:34:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to die outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.46,0:34:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.82,0:34:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.65,0:34:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.75,0:34:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon the Generalissimo to enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.92,0:34:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.70,0:34:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.92,0:34:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon the Generalissimo\Nto enter the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, don't enter the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.97,0:35:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.82,0:35:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager's edict must be\NZhāng Ràng and Duàn Guī's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.72,0:35:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,General you mustn't go inside,\Nthere will surely be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.85,0:35:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous, my very own sister summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.77,0:35:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What can go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.15,0:35:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo, the order for\N frontier troops must have leaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.45,0:35:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We are exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.57,0:35:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we still enter the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To meet the Empress Dowager, you must first\Nsummon all the eunuchs out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.20,0:35:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An act of lesser men! I hold the power of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.82,0:35:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What could the Ten Attendants dare do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.55,0:35:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,\Nif you insist on going, we will come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.87,0:35:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.50,0:35:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.75,0:35:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.32,0:36:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empress Dowager summons only the Generalissimo, no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold the supreme power of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.60,0:36:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Zhāng Ràng, Duàn Guī,\Nand the others dare do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.17,0:37:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,\Nplease board your carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.72,0:37:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo,\Nplease board your carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.12,0:37:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Generalissimo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.66,0:37:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The eunuchs have murdered a high official!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me! We will enter the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.50,0:37:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the eunuchs!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.95,0:37:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager, it's an emergency, quickly follow your ministers to escape the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.52,0:37:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.42,0:37:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.75,0:37:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.70,0:37:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.40,0:37:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere,\Nlet go of me! Someone, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.50,0:37:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, this way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.47,0:38:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.40,0:38:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.37,0:38:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.42,0:38:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.75,0:38:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.00,0:38:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Empress Dowager
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.12,0:38:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Empress Dowager.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.87,0:38:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We await your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.17,0:38:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Biàn-er?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.07,0:38:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Biàn-er!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.35,0:38:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My son!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.55,0:38:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.07,0:38:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Search and find the Emperor and the Prince of Chénliú!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.45,0:39:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.00,0:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.27,0:39:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.15,0:39:20.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.843,587.045)}Mǐn Gòng
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.42,0:39:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.65,0:39:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.67,0:39:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.02,0:40:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This minister, the Marquis of Áoxiāng and the Overseer of Xīliáng; Dǒng Zhuó has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.60,0:40:07.80,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.863,705.682)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: Zǐshī
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.10,0:40:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Dǒng Zhuó?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.67,0:40:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This minister is Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.87,0:40:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when the Yellow Turbans rebelled, you were defeated and suffered heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.90,0:40:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of your guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.24,0:40:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This minister confesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.75,0:40:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The new regime is still young
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.54,0:40:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you came just in time for the rescue,\Ndoing us a great service.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.34,0:40:27.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(201.763,664.773)\fade(255,0,255,0,550,1650,1940)}Lǐ Rú
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:28.47,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1209.559,711.818)}Lǐ Sù
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.26,0:40:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you have to make up your previous actions by doing good deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.98,0:40:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.95,0:40:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This minister will do everything\Nhe can to assist the Imperial Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.63,0:40:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Escort us to the palace.
